channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] watsonx Code Assistant (code-assistant) has changed the description of the plan named essentials-z
item.description: *before*: The Essentials plan for IBM watsonx Code Assistant for Z as a Service, coupled with watsonx Code Assistant for Z (on prem), offers everything you need to translate COBOL to Java., *after*: The Essentials plan for IBM watsonx Code Assistant for Z as a Service, coupled with watsonx code Assistant for Z (on prem), offers everything you need to explain code and translate COBOL to Java.
